===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|acord}}, {{term|accord#Middle English|accord}}, {{term|acorden}}, {{term|accorden}}, through {{etyl|fro}} {{term|acort}}, {{term|acorde}}, and {{term|acorder}} (cf. modern French {{term|accord|accord|lang=fr}} and {{term|accorder}}), and in turn from {{etyl|LL.}} {{term|accordo|accordō|lang=la}}, formed from {{etyl|la}}  {{term|ad}} +  {{term|cordis||heart}}.

